description:
Soarin is haunted by a fragment of his alicorn magic he thought he had sealed away. Twilight and Soarin are tasked by Princess Celestia to find this fragment which had taken a physical form, and kill it before all of Equestria is drained of its magic.
Coming June 6th
If you like what I do please consider joining my Patreon! It's the best way to support what I do!
https://www.patreon.com/c/Tamers12345
